2008-05-16 13:31  alexpeshkoff

	* firebird2/src/: include/consts_pub.h (1.19), include/types_pub.h
	(1.10), isql/isql.epp (1.246), jrd/ibase.h (1.135), jrd/svc.cpp
	(1.224), jrd/why.cpp (1.203), jrd/why_proto.h (1.50), qli/dtr.cpp
	(1.50), qli/dtr.h (1.29), qli/err.cpp (1.23), remote/inet.cpp
	(1.242), remote/inet_server.cpp (1.82), remote/serve_proto.h
	(1.14), remote/server.cpp (1.212), remote/os/win32/cntl.cpp (1.41),
	remote/os/win32/srvr_w32.cpp (1.56), remote/os/win32/window.cpp
	(1.33):

	1. Added parameter 'shutdown reason' to fb_shutdown() API call.
	It's passed to shutdown callback function, and helps to take
	correct action in it. This fixes CORE-1827: Win32 Embedded Server
	should pass control to application before calling exit(3).  2.
	Removed unneeded any more flag in isql and qli, used earlier to
	distinguish between kinds of shutdown.

