2008-03-10 10:42  robocop

	* firebird2/src/jrd/: sqz.cpp (1.27), sqz_proto.h (1.13), vio.cpp
	(1.206):

	Cleanup. Done separately in case bad behavior happens.	Notice you
	can't safely assume SCHAR is signed char since Mike Nordell made it
	a synonym for plain char that's compiler-dependent.  SCHAR is
	defined in both types_pub.h and fb_types.h.

